{"tid":415772,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我用figure拍咗一集原創動畫。。。","createTime":"2017-09-27T09:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T15:37:43.000Z","uid":144800,"like":287,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"c99d35ee3a94ca785bdcd05b74f210f2bdb255f0","tid":415772,"uid":144800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rAF-BjeE9gw&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrAF-BjeE9gw%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=1Bsysqd9aMMxOoQO0Q2moE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=84ebde2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rAF-BjeE9gw&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n呢套【廢高俠】係我第一次用綠幕，好多瑕疵，但係我覺得都幾搞嘢<br />\n拍下拍下，竟然拍咗成15分鐘嘅片段<br />\n<br />\n我整咗成7個月, 多得幾個朋友同網友幫我配音，終於完成！<br />\n<br />\n簡介： 一位心地善良但係十下十下嘅青年係偶然間踏上成為超級英雄嘅旅程"},{"pid":"a3fbcbc94fed9afce1091b71e166edb092f69764","tid":415772,"uid":94739,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"支持本地創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：無睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c7420f9d1d5deff776ca68906a9accdd35d9c8","tid":415772,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"Stop motion好花心機，巴打好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f153d82161aa52d3d1a2c9d63cfb9a27c66dda4a","tid":415772,"uid":123390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rAF-BjeE9gw&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrAF-BjeE9gw%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=1Bsysqd9aMMxOoQO0Q2moE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=84ebde2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rAF-BjeE9gw&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"895d291aad3